name: Earth Phase 地相圖 04.22
description: Earth Phase 地相圖 04.22 is a generative art piece inspired by the topic of 2021 Earth Day, "Restore Our Earth." In this artwork , I use live brainwave data to generate a dynamic earth that is self-restored from illness. Artist: UGLYKIKI(Kiki Wu). Created on 04/22/2021. Dimension: 4220 x 3435px.  Half of the proceeds will go to Amazon Conservation Team: https://www.amazonteam.org/.  Celebrate Earth Day and donate to top-rated charities: https://www.charitywatch.org/top-rated-charities/environment
